    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s not just a phase though. it feels more permanent than that. like the engine has actually died. if the thing that made me \"me\" is gone, what actually remains? just this heavy, useless weight of a body that keeps moving even though there's nothing driving it anymore.",
